_sText:
This is the first real map I've made, and I learned a lot in the process of making it.
It's a trikz map with medium/hard difficulty, which is intended to be played on servers with the no-bug plugin.

The map includes:
- 22 levels with increasing difficulty + numerous solo-levels
- A bonus longjump room as well as a bonus area with X3 to X7
- An end room with 5 different songs to choose from
- A couple of secrets

Note: The map has been updated with some fixes and changes, and is now called **trikz_diversity_final**.

Trikz_cooperation is the first map trikz which has been created. It is through it that the team Trikz and Terracid have gained notoriety. This map using textures development consists of various rooms, each offering a mission to players. As its name suggests, this map was designed to be played at two minimum, in cooperation. The principle of each room is very simple: you must cross barriers by various means, to achieve a button, which opens the door, and you will therefore reach the next room. Like all such successors, this map calls on players to use their expertise in the jump to clear the obstacles.

Hello Trikzor!


Compiled in:

- HDR FULL COMPILE
- Added all the textures

Theme  Levels:

- Portal
- Izi Aztec
- Lego
- Dev Color
- Color

Total:

- 38 main levels
- Bonus (Bh; Lj; Rb; Gb; Normal Bonus LvL)
- There is a big box with Rb up to 602 units, just sky and longjamp up to 270

Difficulties:

There are no separate levels in a separate box, only a linear map. Levels are made on the level of complexity, the further the more difficult.

Sound:

- Music Secret Start
- Music Main End
- Music Bonus End

Test map:

Are inscribed at the very end of the map.

Edit:

- When you turn on the music on the button, whoever uses snd_restart will no longer be turned on.
- When you turn on the music on the button, it will not play or overlap.
- When you turn on the music on the button for other music, it will replace the previous one or start playing first, there will be no drawdowns fps will also not be included if the player used snd_restart.

I wish you success!

Hello!

I give you my second card for joint passage.

On this map are all the complexities of the complex, from the simplest to the most complex. There is both sovmesnoe passage, and one pass.

There are enough levels on the map to play it with interest.

When all levels of the map pass, there is a bonus solo level.

At the very beginning, before the longjump 250 there is a passage back called Noob Music Zone with the height of blocks of 66 units, in the zone there is a button with random musical performance in 30 seconds, rising from Noob Music Zone you can simply jump and gain speed, and in the center of the corridor there is a picture, In which you can go in and it will find 2 buttons, 1 button to turn on 1 music, and the second to turn it off.

At the end of the card there are 3 buttons, 2 of them include music on the entire map, 1 for turning off the music.

When you turn on the song, the player displays the song title in the center of the screen.

Also, when passing Solo level there is a button for turning on music and turning off!

The design and textures on the map look in the colors of the rainbow, and look very cool.

I really hope that you will enjoy playing on my map!

For those who saw the map before release: 

The map removed complex levels, as well as the last 4 levels removed due to the fact that the map is too huge, because of the huge number of obscenities the game took off, and so the server did not deal with the oversupply of lighting! Thus, I decided to remove enough levels that the map would be playable, but I want to report that the levels have been saved and will be added to my next map, but it will be more difficult!

First I must say I have atrx's permission for editing this map. All credit goes to him for making this map. I just wanted to add the timer so people could possibly try speedruns in it.

Map trikz_4teams_beta12 is really old map and its one of my favorites.

My original plan was to just add the timer. Then I decided to change couple of other things, nothing drastic. I know the map has a lot of extra space, but I wanted to keep it really close to the original because I liked the open feel of it.

Changes from trikz_4teams_beta12:

- added timer and implemented a good way for it to work on a trikz map
- optimized with func_detail + nodraw
- fit stuff more to grid
- added env_light and lights
- minor gameplay changes and bug fixes (faster flash spawn, flash delete, ladder works now and last levels teleport works)
